<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <%- include('./partials/head'); %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/videoGallery.css">
</head>

<body id="page-top">
    <!-- Navigation-->
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg fixed-top" id="mainNav">
        <%- include('./partials/topmenu'); %>
    </nav>


    <!-- Page Content -->
    <section class="page-section page-section-top-padded mb-0" id="about">
        <div class="container">

            <div id="all-gallery">
                <h1>Welcome to the Roots Floral video gallery!</h1>
                <div class="main-text">At Roots Floral, we are passionate about sharing the beauty and artistry of floral design with everyone. Our collection of YouTube videos is designed to inspire and guide you through the intricate world of floral arrangements. Whether you’re a novice looking to explore a new hobby or an experienced florist seeking fresh ideas, our step-by-step tutorials offer something for everyone.</div>

                <div class="main-text">Our expert florist, Yolanta, has created a series of engaging and easy-to-follow videos that cover a wide range of styles and techniques. From creating stunning bouquets and centerpieces to mastering the art of flower arrangement, our tutorials are designed to help you unleash your creativity and achieve beautiful results. Follow along at your own pace and discover the joy of floral design with Roots Floral.</div>
                    
                <div class="main-text">Explore our video gallery below and click on any thumbnail to watch the full tutorial on YouTube. Don’t forget to subscribe to our channel to stay updated with our latest videos and tips. Happy arranging!</div>
                <div class="video-gallery-container">
                    <% videos.forEach(video => { %>
                        <div class="video-gallery-item">
                            <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=<%= video.videoId %>" target="_blank">
                                <img src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/<%= video.videoId %>/hqdefault.jpg" alt="<%= video.title %>">
                                <h2><%= video.title %></h2>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    <% }); %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer-->
    <%- include('./partials/footer'); %>
    <!-- Copyright Section-->
    <%- include('./partials/copyright'); %>
    <!-- Scroll to Top Button (Only visible on small and extra-small screen sizes)-->
    <div class="scroll-to-top d-lg-none position-fixed">
        <a class="js-scroll-trigger d-block text-center text-white rounded" href="#page-top"><i
                class="fa fa-chevron-up"></i></a>
    </div>


    <%- include('./partials/jsincludes'); %>
    <script src="/js/videoGallery.js"></script>
</body>

</html>







